9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"The Jungle Book | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"A man-cub named Mowgli fostered by wolves. After a threat from the tiger Shere Khan, Mowgli is forced to flee the jungle, by which he embarks on a journey of self discovery with the help of the panther, Bagheera and the free-spirited bear, Baloo."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/106051/the-jungle-book"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"The Jungle Book"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"A man-cub named Mowgli fostered by wolves. After a threat from the tiger Shere Khan, Mowgli is forced to flee the jungle, by which he embarks on a journey of self discovery with the help of the panther, Bagheera and the free-spirited bear, Baloo."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/106051/the-jungle-book"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2Epx7F9X7DrFptn4seqn4mzBVks.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"The Jungle Book"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"A man-cub named Mowgli fostered by wolves. After a threat from the tiger Shere Khan, Mowgli is forced to flee the jungle, by which he embarks on a journey of self discovery with the help of the panther, Bagheera and the free-spirited bear, Baloo."}],["$","meta","13",{"name":"twitter:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2Epx7F9X7DrFptn4seqn4mzBVks.jpg"}],["$","link","14",{"rel":"icon","href":"/favicon.svg"}],["$","$L16","15",{}]],"error":null,"